OL,4,CAKO Caine Prize: Meron Hadero named
OL,5,Cfirst Ethiopian winner
OL,6, Meron Hadero has become the first
OL,7, Ethiopian author to win the prestigious
OL,8, AKO Caine Prize for African Writing.
OL,10,F"I'm absolutely thrilled, I'm in shock
OL,11,F- being shortlisted in itself was a
OL,12,Fhuge honour," she told the BBC.
OL,14,FHer winning short story is about an
OL,15,FEthiopian boy called Getu, who has to
OL,16,Fnavigate the fraught power dynamics of
OL,17,FNGOs and foreign aid in Addis Ababa.
OL,19,FIt impressed the judges who found it
OL,20,F"utterly without self-pity" and said it
OL,21,F"turns the lens" on the usual cliches.
